Name: Home Health Care Eligible Services

Name: Home Health Care

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Up to 10 Combined Visits per incident.  Number of Visits will be reduced by any Physical, Occupational and/or Speech Therapy received under Home Health Care Services. Maximum Reasonable Guidelines apply to Out-of-Network Expenses.
Name: Outpatient Therapy: Physical, Occupational, and Speech Therapy Limits

%vlocity_namespace%__AttributeDisplayNam: Outpatient Therapy: Physical, Occupational, and Speech Therapy
%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: For conditions related to an eligible diagnosis of OT, PT and/or ST performed by a licensed therapist expenses are Eligible for Sharing after a $20 Visit Fee, per visit up to the Maximum Limit Per Incident.
Name: Outpatient Therapy: Physical, Occupational, and Speech Therapy

%vlocity_namespace%__Value__c: Listed Preventive Services and one Wellness Visit : Eligible Expenses 100% Shared up to $1,000 Maximum per program year
Name: Preventive Services and Wellness Visit

Name: Primary Care Physician Visit Limit:

Name: Primary Care Physician Visit

Name: Surgery
